      "body" : "@RashmiRanjanmallick they both are almost similar, with the only difference being that in Json, forward-slash (/) is escaped. You can use any of them, however, if you&#39;re intending to use it with some JSON parser, then it&#39;s better to use <code>escapeJson()</code> method."
